From: "bridgetvic1964" <razemfamily@...>

I think I know what the curfew thing was about.It's about control,or
imagined control.It made things easier for me to know that my son was
home safe and sound.The whole thing is about me,it's always about
me,me,me.I think I have definite control issues,ewwwww!Bad Mommy:-)
